---
import App from "../components/app";
import Header from "../components/header";
import Blade from "../components/blade/blade";
import IconWithHint from "../components/icon-with-hint";
---

<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
		<meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
		<meta
			name="description"
			content="JM's landing page. A guy that exists is here"
		/>
		<title>JM's Landing Page</title>
	</head>
	<body>
		<App>
			<Header client:load />
			
			<Blade type="right">
				<h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-center">Welcome Wanderer</h2>
				<p>
					Just some socials for Jose Marco who also goes by JM.
				</p>
			</Blade>
			
			<Blade type="left">
				<section class="w-max flex align-middle justify-center">
					<IconWithHint
						client:visible
						message="@nglr_jm"
						size={24}
						src="/icons/002-youtube.png"
						alt="youtube icon"
						href="https://www.youtube.com/@nglr_jm"
						hint="Check a video of mine"
					/>
				</section>
				<p>
					There's a youtube I own you can subscribe to if you so wish to. Though
					really it's random content that I have there with no real upload schedule.
				</p>
			</Blade>

			<Blade type="right">
				<section class="w-max flex align-middle justify-center">
					<IconWithHint
						client:visible
						message="@jmnuf"
						size={24}
						src="/icons/003-github.png"
						alt="github icon"
						href="https://github.com/jmnuf/"
						hint="Check some code of mine"
					/>
				</section>
				<p>
					I have github with some random projects I've worked on. Consider taking a look there if you wish to. <br />
					This website is also publicly available in the <a href="https://github.com/jmnuf/jm-on-site">github</a> if you so wish to see the source code
				</p>
			</Blade>

			<Blade type="left">
				<section class="w-max flex align-middle justify-center">
					<IconWithHint
						client:visible
						message="@jm_of_nglr"
						size={24}
						src="/icons/001-twitch.png"
						alt="twitch icon"
						href="https://twitch.tv/jm_of_nglr"
						hint="Catch some live of mine"
					/>
				</section>
				<p>
					Though not really a habit I do stream sometimes, have done code, art and games streams.<br />
					I do work a full time so if I do stream I'lll usually do so either a Saturday or Sunday at around 15:30~16:30 CET or 3:30pm~4:30pm for those that don't know 24hrs.<br />
					This website was started in a live stream actually!
				</p>
			</Blade>
		</App>
	</body>
</html>
